reviewText: Hero Ships is average documentary.  I expected more as in Battle 360. Or even the Dogfight series.  Will pass on any more in this series.
Title: History Classics: Hero Ships

reviewText: I was really proud of these DVDs. It lets you know about what these ships went through during their days of activeness while serving our great nation. And what it took to fight on the oceans.
summary: Great naval History of these ships
Title: History Classics: Hero Ships

reviewText: if you're a navy fan, this compilation is a must ! Very informative, interesting and covers everything from the Constitution on to nuclear powered submarines.
Title: History Classics: Hero Ships

reviewText: This set includes a bunch of different Navy vessels that fought bravely in WWII.  Very detailed information from the History Channel.  Most of the ships are now floating museums for you to see.  Felt I got more than I expected from this set.
summary: Great 4-disc set of some historical naval vessels of WWII !
Title: History Classics: Hero Ships

reviewText: This is an excellent compilation of some of the greatest warships. Indeed "Hero" warships. I think anyone who has an interest in military history will enjoy this .
Title: History Classics: Hero Ships
